# Splint Geo Processor - Secret
#
# This is the ONLY file you create on a new deployment.
# All other settings are in .env.local (Mac) or .env.production (Windows),
# which are committed to git.
#
# Get your API key from the factory admin UI at /admin/api-keys
SF_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
